contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary|Zentrum}} '''Zentrum''' is [[German language|German]] for '''centre'''. It may refer to: * [[Centre Party (Germany)|Zentrumspartei]] or Centre Party, a political party in Germany. * ETH Zentrum, a central campus of [[ETH Zurich]] * [[BMW Manufacturing Co. Spartanburg|BMW Zentrum]], a BMW museum in [[Spartanburg, South Carolina]] * [[Arginine|Zentrum]], a brand name for the amino acid Arginine 1200 mg. * [[Center (group theory)|Centre of a group]], denoted <math>Z(G)</math> from the German name {{disambig}}
